---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="Erik Knuppel">
  <section class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black leading-tight mb-6">
      Ops leader. Former lawyer.<br />Teacher. Builder.
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-ink-light leading-relaxed mb-8">
      I work at the intersection of tech, marketplaces, and revenue operations — with a background in law, teaching, and competitive advocacy. Based in San Francisco.
    </p>
    <p class="text-ink-light leading-relaxed mb-10">
      Currently driving bookings growth at <a href="https://karat.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-ink font-semibold hover:text-warm transition-colors">Karat</a>, where I use AI to automate outbound/inbound intelligence and empower sellers at scale. Previously built and scaled ops and analytics functions across high-growth marketplaces.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 mb-16">
      <a href="/mocktrial" class="group flex items-center gap-3 text-ink font-semibold hover:text-warm transition-colors">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-cream-dark text-earth text-sm group-hover:bg-gold group-hover:text-ink transition-colors">MT</span>
        Urban School Mock Trial Program
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/erikknuppel/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="group flex items-center gap-3 text-ink font-semibold hover:text-warm transition-colors">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-cream-dark text-earth text-sm group-hover:bg-gold group-hover:text-ink transition-colors">Li</span>
        LinkedIn
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-cream-dark pt-8">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-4">Background</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-sm text-ink-light leading-relaxed">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Revenue & Operations</h3>
          <p>Marketplace ops, RevOps, analytics, and GTM strategy across startups and growth-stage companies.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Law & Advocacy</h3>
          <p>Former trial and appellate attorney. 10+ years teaching trial advocacy at the law school level. Founded GavelStats, a mock trial analytics platform.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Teaching & Coaching</h3>
          <p>Adjunct professor at UC Law SF and Golden Gate Law. 20+ competition teams coached. Launching a high school mock trial program.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Building</h3>
          <p>AI-powered workflows, data systems, and side projects — always looking for the leverage point where tech meets human judgment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
